    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "In Flight with TWA...\nTWA'S\nSuper-Constellation\nSKYLINER\nYou enjoy luxury living\naloft as you fly\nsmoothly in TWA's\ndependable, giant new\nSuper-Constellation\nSkyliners,\nthe latest word\nin swift, modern\npassenger aircraft.\nTWA\nTRANS WORLD AIRLINES\nU. S. A.\nEUROPE\nAFRA",
